      "raw_text": "Mayor Boyd received q telegram\nthis afternoon from W.. A. Aldrich,\nmanager of the Spokane Falls Gas\ncompany, who is In Portland, offering\nthe city site for the Carnegie\nlibrary\n\n\nMr.. Aldrich stated the city could\nhave half of the company's property\nat the northwest corner of Riverside\navenue and Monroe street for tI2,oeo."
